{"tid":344984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那駐洛衫磯領事館遭連發18鎗襲擊","createTime":"2017-08-02T16:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T16:10:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e72de70280c4c0dfcc638ae09bc4963a3aef7845","tid":344984,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"SOURCE: <a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-40798996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-40798996&d=PbC1aPS5YihWYmaKu%2BFY7AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0f6a4d9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-40798996&h=17dc40a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-40798996</a><br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯警局:中國總領館襲擊者為亞裔男子 年齡名字不明<br />\n2017年 8月 2日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/129AE/production/_97160267_hi040884670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F660%2Fcpsprodpb%2F129AE%2Fproduction%2F_97160267_hi040884670.jpg&h=f6128366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國駐美國洛杉磯總領事館周二（8月1日）早上發生一宗槍擊案，一名亞裔男子在領館門外前掃射多槍，然後吞槍自殺。<br />\n<br />\n洛杉磯警局發言人對BBC中文網說，現時只確定槍手為亞裔男子，未知道他的年齡、名字。<br />\n<br />\n「他們（到場時）在車廂中找到一名亞裔男子，有自己造成的槍傷。當場被證實死亡，這就是我們現知的事實。」<br />\n<br />\n「案件調查仍然在進行中。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/8D6E/production/_97160263_hi040884912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F8D6E%2Fproduction%2F_97160263_hi040884912.jpg&h=d78c40aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《星島日報》報道，槍手為一名60多歲的華裔男子，他駕駛一輛銀灰色豐田凱美瑞，在領事館門外掃射多槍。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，現場可見最少有七枚子彈從玻璃窗射入，而另外有幾枚子彈打在外牆及門牌。<br />\n<br />\n《僑報網》報道指，槍手一共發射18枚子彈。"}]}